{"tid":1415781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你地 家陣習慣左？屌你地！","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T14:40:59.000Z","uid":38165,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b3e1d23fe9101728c172458f1f3a4006b01d0256","tid":1415781,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:10:33.000Z","msg":"《習慣說》，不要<br />\n習慣就是默認結果向著差的方向發展<br />\n<br />\n轉帖<br />\n//香港人遊行第一次食催淚彈，全世界都覺得好離譜；<br />\n<br />\n現在，我們已慣了遊行一定會出催淚彈，就算無人衝擊都會射，現在看的，是幾多粒；<br />\n<br />\n然後是橡膠彈、布袋彈、什至海綿彈；<br />\n<br />\n我們不再驚訝警方會出呢d , 我們習慣了，人們會覺得射得5，6粒，少左、寬容左；<br />\n<br />\n錯了，一粒，一粒都是太多！<br />\n<br />\n有一天，我們可能會講又有示威者被打死了，今次死一個，算少了.....<br />\n<br />\n這就是中共/北韓政府最擅長的，用強權壓制，令大部分人麻目，讓你忘記本身的權利，讓覺得有口水飲的也是他們的恩賜。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位唔可以習慣，我覺得大家已經麻目啦</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求下你地醒下啦，天埼同我地講過唔可以比仇恨沖昏頭腦！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地係味應該講下下一步行動？民間記者會？文宣？機場？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重申再次：核彈都唔撚割！一毛黑警死全家</span></span>"},{"pid":"f05c9d1be0e3da89567940ab9786daa82723cf4f","tid":1415781,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"手土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19a31f6b967a8a61e3b4d0b04d0c491d0741bc0","tid":1415781,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:11:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1656859dcebc0ab489a798ab0985c43f91bdef1","tid":1415781,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:12:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b62125fc1d2f2f19c3d149d43c4cbc05d7bd96c","tid":1415781,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:14:27.000Z